address2: 6th Floor Jalan H.R. Rasuna Said Kav. B1
longBusinessSummary: PT Bakrieland Development Tbk operates as an integrated property company in Indonesia. The company develops and sells urban properties, landed residential estates, office buildings, malls / commercial areas, hotels, and resorts as well as theme parks, and food courts; rents and manages offices, spaces, and courts; manages the shopping centers, theme parks, and recreation parks; and operates and manages hotels. It is also involved in the trading, investment, and refinancing businesses; and management of recreation and tourism areas, a sport center, buildings, apartments, and residential areas. In addition, the company engages in the construction of accommodation buildings, highways, roads, hotels, vilas, restaurants, cafes, tourism areas, educational buildings, offices, lodgings, entertainment and sports facilities, shopping, and other buildings. Further, it is involved in the fixed-time labor; facility support services; private security and security system services; garden care and maintenance; real estate land preparation; installation of waterways; building and other industrial cleaning; food and beverage services; parking; and wireless telecommunication activities. The company was formerly known as PT Elang Realty Tbk. and changed its name to PT Bakrieland Development Tbk. in April 1997. PT Bakrieland Development Tbk was founded in 1990 and is headquartered in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia.
